snippet.title: Alice Cooper says Johnny Depp has never looked better and press coverage is ‘total bull’
snippet.description:
VideoImage
Johnny Depp suing ex-wife Amber Heard for $70million 0:27
Actor Johnny Depp is taking legal action against his ex-wife Amber Heard accusing her of defamation. An article in the Washington Post, written by Heard, detailed the backlash she faced after speaking out about domestic violence. Mr Depp's lawsuit says he 'never abused Ms Heard' and says the claims are 'part of an elaborate hoax' to advance her career. He is seeking more than $70 million in damages. 
March 3rd 201910 days ago/display/newscorpaustralia.com/Web/NewsNetwork/Entertainment - syndicated/
Alice Cooper said negative reports about the finances and wellbeing of Johnny Depp are false. Picture: Mark CallejaSource:News Corp Australia 
Johnny Depp’s friend and bandmate Alice Cooper has come to his defence amid a number of unfavourable headlines, saying negative press surrounding the actor is “just bull”.
